SELECT DATE_TRUNC('day', view_date) AS timestamp,
       name AS name,
       SUM(cast(total_video_views as decimal)) as Total_video_view
FROM public."smg_dmp_fb_video_dashboard_unq"
JOIN
  (SELECT name AS name__,
          SUM(cast(total_video_views as decimal)) AS mme_inner__
   FROM public."smg_dmp_fb_video_dashboard_unq"
   GROUP BY name
   ORDER BY mme_inner__ DESC
   LIMIT 100) AS anon_1 ON name = name__
GROUP BY name,timestamp
ORDER BY Total_video_view DESC
LIMIT 30;
